                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="arial" size="2" color="#000000"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> The white and black stallions (Lithiniath) can be pet tanked by chain casting tod and lighting them up with fp and pyro. Lithiniath is a much longer fight than the white stallion though. <br /><br />However, I have not been able to successfully kill the white Lithiniath (spawned by turning in  Lithiniath's Horn to the White Stallion) which cons yellow to a 65. <br /><br />I have killed both stallions at least 6 times in the last month and no cards have dropped off of them (thrones are rumored to drop), but Lithiniath usually drops 4 high level velious spells and other random loot (bd, fd, vendor jewelry, etc.) so its well worth the fight. <br /><br />I am almost done with my sojourn in mischief, just need a white crown to finish my last flower. Good luck on your journey.. it is a fun zone.<br /></span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
