                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="arial" size="2" color="#000000"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> Thrones : best chances are the treasure chests, AiW4, white stallion, puppets<br />Crown : AiW, chessboards, white stallion, treasure chests, puppets<br />Knight : chessboards, puppets, theater, about any random mobs in castle<br />Squires : Forrest, audience, puppets, random mobs in castle<br />Jester : My Right Hand (never seen other mobs dropping it so far)<br /><br />King cod card : Dinner, fished in the moat<br />to obtain the deck of spontaneous generation, you need either a KCC, or the 4 color cod card(fished only) and turn it/them to ferjenor in the garden<br /><br />Library Card : from any gorilla, from east wing or chessboard<br />Book of mischief : turn a library card to Posie the librarian in the ... Library<br /><br />Words of Wealth : parts drop from any mobs (top left, top right, bottom left, bottom right) combine the 4 parts in the book of mischief to create the WoW<br /><br />Empty Pot'o'Gold : turn a WoW to Bob the Painter in the main room<br />Funny money : combine a WoW with a quest item in the empty Pot'o'Gold (Top left works also)<br /><br />Hand 2 funny money to peaches at castle entrance to receive a class doll, with 5 charges (it's lore, and you may get 2 same in row, be careful)<br /><br />Jester have no use found so far<br />My right Hand : killed him with a shaman, i was 63 and shaman was 65, resisted slow twice, but then, it was cake, he was still hitting fast though</span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
